# orchestrator — decision log

Kept by the orchestrating session on the same append-only discipline as
every agent's build.log. Records every merge decision (task ID, which
`tester`/`adversarial-generalist` gate entries were verified before
merging), every escalation raised or resolved, and every
significant/minor-finding call made and why. This exists so a resumed or
replacement orchestrator session — or the human, auditing after the
fact — has continuity instead of reconstructing "why was this merged"
from five other logs and git history. Newest entries at the bottom. Do
not delete or rewrite prior entries.

